description:
Issue 3 of 3 of Touch of Death a comic book mini-series from Brain Scan Studios.

The conclusion of the series, with 32 pages of Touch of Death! Left to enter the underground base by himself, Michael quickly realizes that he may have to kill in order to save his wife; will he be able to do it? All loose ends come together in this explosive finale! By Brian Kirsten, Ray Dillon and GW Fisher with cover by Andrew Robinson. Plus, this issue includes &quot;Epiphany&quot; an 8-page short story by Brian Kirsten, Erich Owen and Jim Keplinger. 

